---
import Headline from "../components/Headline.astro";
import TableRow from "../components/TableRow.astro";
import LayoutCV from "../layouts/LayoutCV.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
---

<LayoutCV title="CV">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-3 items-center mb-6 md:mb-12">
    <img
      class="col-span-1 rounded-full w-20 h-20 md:w-32 md:h-32 border-4 border-primary"
      src="/benedictbihlmaier.webp"
      alt="Portrait von Benedict Bihlmaier"
    />
    <div class="col-span-2">
      <h1 class="text-xl mb-2 md:text-4xl md:mb-4 font-medium">
        Benedict Bihlmaier
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm md:text-base flex items-center">
        <Icon
          aria-hidden="true"
          focusable="false"
          class="inline-block w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-primary"
          pack="mdi"
          name="email"
        />
        <a class="hover:text-primary" href="mailto:Benedict.Bihlmaier@gmail.com"
          >Benedict.Bihlmaier@gmail.com</a
        >
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <Headline headingLevel="h2" icon="account">Profile</Headline>
  <p>
    With a background in human-computer interaction, I have been working in
    digital product and service development since 2017. I started to focus on
    web development during my studies and complement this skillset with broad
    knowledge in user experience design. The desire for variety and challenges
    led me to the agency world. From here I can look back on project experience
    in various industries like automotive, med-tech, public sector, and others.
    My activities include writing, testing, and reviewing code (primarily
    React.js + Typescript) as well as mentoring junior colleagues and working
    closely with designers. I see myself as a motivated, communicative
    bridge-builder between disciplines with strong roots in front-end
    development.
  </p>
  <Headline headingLevel="h2" icon="briefcase">Experience</Headline>

  <table class="block overflow-x-auto md:table md:border-spacing-4">
    <TableRow
      date="05/2019 - heute"
      location="Munich"
      company="designaffairs GmbH / Accenture (seit 09/21)"
      title="Senior Creative Technologist"
      list={[
        "Hybrid role focusing on frontend development with particular attention to working closely with other disciplines such as UI and UX design.",
        "Developing frontend code for prototypes to enterprise applications with multiple teams in an agile way.",
        "Ensuring Accessibility and Performance in Design and Development.",
        "Responsible for architecture and implementation of various deliverables (e.g. web-based design systems).",
        "Mentoring of colleagues",
      ]}
    />
    <TableRow
      date="04/2018 - 09/2018"
      location="Munich"
      company="designaffairs GmbH"
      title="Intern Interaction Technology"
      list={[
        "Creation of UX concepts (wireframing, user journey mapping, etc.)",
        "Web-based prototyping (JavaScript and Vue.js)",
        "Conducting co-creation workshops with clients",
      ]}
    />
    <TableRow
      date="05/2017 - 01/2019"
      location="Würzburg"
      company="webfellows UG"
      title="Working Student Frontend Development"
      list={[
        "Development of templates for online stores based on the eCommerce system Shopware",
        "Conceptual and design work as well as implementation using common web technologies (JavaScript, Smarty/HTML, LESS)",
        "Backend-oriented work within the Shopware environment. This included the development of plugins to extend the store functionality using technologies such as PHP and ExtJs.",
      ]}
    />
  </table>

  <Headline headingLevel="h2" icon="school">Education</Headline>

  <table class="block overflow-x-auto md:table md:border-spacing-4">
    <TableRow
      date="2015 - 2019"
      location="Würzburg"
      company="Julius-Maximilians-Universität"
      title="Mensch-Computer-Systeme (Human-Computer-Systems) B.Sc."
      list={[
        "MCS is a hybrid major that combines computer science with psychology and interdisciplinary courses.",
        "Final grade: 1.7",
      ]}
    />
  </table>

  <Headline headingLevel="h2" icon="lightbulb">Skills</Headline>
  <h3 class="text-lg mb-1 font-semibold">Core</h3>
  <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-2">
    <li>Typescript</li>
    <li>JavaScript</li>
    <li>(Semantic) HTML</li>
    <li>CSS/SCSS/Tailwind</li>
    <li>User Experience</li>
    <li>Versioning (Git)</li>
    <li>React.js</li>
    <li>Next.js</li>
    <li>Node.js</li>
    <li>Agile Development</li>
  </ul>
  <h3 class="text-lg mb-1 mt-6 font-semibold">Adjacent</h3>

  <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-2">
    <li>User Research</li>
    <li>Wireframing</li>
    <li>Accessibility</li>
    <li>Technical Writing</li>
    <li>Python</li>
    <li>Vue.js</li>
    <li>Serverless</li>
  </ul>
</LayoutCV>
